    "causal_summary": "Run the bespoke deep-loop. Each iteration picks a council-seeded variant or mutates the current best along one axis, dispatches cli-devin against SWE 1.6 for each fixture (parallel wave of 3), scores via the 002 rig (deterministic + grader, cached), aggregates a variant score, then evaluates convergence via 3-signal weighted vote. Loop legal-stops when stopScore > 0.60 AND coverage + quality + budget gates pass. Min 6 iterations. Synthesis ranks variants with confidence scores and key insights. Output is `synthesis.md` — the binding handoff for 004 to apply winners.",
